<h1>Add a New Sneaker to Your Closet</h1><br>
<form method="POST" action="/sneakers">
    Brand: <input type="text" name="brand"><br><br>
    Model: <input type="text" name="model"><br><br>
    Sport: <input type="text" name="sport"><br><br>
    Price: <input type="float" name="price"><br><br>
    Size:  <input type="float" name="size"><br><br>
    <input type="submit" value="Create sneaker!">
</form>
<br>
<li><h5>Or <a href="/sneakers">click here to go back to your closet.</a></h5></li>
